window.locale({"domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural_forms":"nplurals=4; plural=(n%100==1 ? 0 : n%100==2 ? 1 : n%100>=3 && n%100<=4 ? 2 : 3);","lang":"sl"},"About Twine":["O programu"],"Twine is an open-source tool for telling interactive, nonlinear stories.":["Twine je odprtokodno orodje za pripovedovanje interaktivnih nelinearnih zgodb."],"This application is released under the \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html\">GPL v3\\x3c/a> license, but any work created with it may be released under any terms, including commercial ones.":["Ta program je izdan pod licenco \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html\">GPL v3\\x3c/a>, toda vsa dela, izdelana z njim, lahko izdate pod kakršnimi koli pogoji, tudi komercialnimi."],"Help Twine Grow With A Donation":["Pomagajte pri razvoju z donacijo"],"Source Code Repository":["Repozitorij izvorne kode"],"Translations":["Prevodi"],"Libraries":["Knjižnice"],"Fonts":["Pisave"],"Source Sans Pro and Source Code Pro were designed by Paul D. Hunt under the guidance of Robert Slimbach for \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/adobe.com/\">Adobe\\x3c/a>\\x3cbr> Nunito was designed by \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/code.newtypography.co.uk/\">Vernon Adams\\x3c/a>":["Source Sans Pro in Source Code Pro je oblikoval Paul D. Hunt s podporo Roberta Slimbacha za \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/adobe.com/\">Adobe\\x3c/a>\\x3cbr> Nunito je oblikoval \\x3ca href=\"http:\\/\\/code.newtypography.co.uk/\">Vernon Adams\\x3c/a>"],"Icons":["Ikone"],"Document designed by Rob Gill from the Noun Project":["Document je ustvaril Rob Gill iz Noun Projecta"],"Question designed by Henry Ryder from the Noun Project":["Question je ustvaril Henry Ryder iz Noun Projecta"],"Smile designed by jelio dimitrov from the Noun Project":["Smile je ustvaril jelio Dimitrov iz Noun Projecta"],"If you love Twine as much as I do, please consider helping it grow with a donation. Twine is an open source project that will always be free to use &mdash; and with your help, Twine will continue to thrive.":["Če vam je Twine všeč toliko kot meni, lahko kaj prispevate za njegov razvoj. Twine je odprtokodni projekt, ki bo vedno brezplačen &mdash; in z vašo pomočjo bo še naprej lahko cvetel."],"Chris Klimas, Twine creator":["Chris Klimas, ustvarjalec Twinea"],"No Thanks":["Ne, hvala"],"Donate":["Prispevaj"],"This message will only be shown to you once.&lt;br&gt;If you'd like to donate to Twine development in the future, you can do so at &lt;a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/twinery.org/donate\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;http://twinery.org/donate&lt;/a&gt;.":["To sporočilo bo prikazano samo enkrat.&lt;br&gt;Če boste kdaj pozneje želeli prispevati k razvoju Twinea, lahko obiščete spletno mesto &lt;a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/twinery.org/donate\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;http://twinery.org/donate&lt;/a&gt;."],"Story formats control the appearance and behavior of stories during play.":["Zgodbeni formati nadzorujejo videz in obnašanje zgodb med predvajanjem."],"Use as Default":["Uporabi kot privzeto"],"Proofing formats create a versions of stories tailored for editing and proofreading.":["Korekturni formati ustvarijo različice zgodb, ki so primerne za urejanje in korekture."],"Use":["Uporabi"],"Add":["Dodaj"],"Loading...":["Nalagam..."],"Story Format":["Format zgodbe"],"A story format controls the appearance and behavior of your story during play.":["Zgodbeni format nadzoruje videz in obnašanje vaše zgodbe med predvajanjem."],"Import From File":["Uvozi iz datoteke"],"Import this file:":["Uvozi to datoteko:"],"Cancel":["Prekliči"],"Working...":["V obdelavi..."],"Some stories you are importing already exist in your library. Please choose which to replace. Any other stories in your file will be imported as well.":["Nekaj zgodb, ki jih uvažate, že obstaja v vaši knjižnici. Prosim, izberite, katere naj bodo zamenjane. Vse ostale zgodbe v vaši datoteki bodo prav tako uvožene."],"Don't Import Any Stories":["Ne uvozi nobenih zgodb"],"Find and Replace":["Najdi in zamenjaj"],"Search For":["Išči"],"Include passage names":["Vključi imena prehodov"],"Match case":["Ujemanje malih/velikih črk"],"Regular expression":["Regularni izraz"],"Replace With":["Zamenjaj z"],"Replace All":["Zamenjaj vse"],"%d passage matches.":["%d prehod se ujema.","%d prehoda se ujemata.","%d prehodi se ujemajo.","%d prehodov se ujema."],"Searching...":["Iščem..."],"%d match":["%d zadetek","%d zadetka","%d zadetki","%d zadetkov"],"Replace in Passage":["Zamenjaj v prehodu"],"Story Statistics":["Statistika zgodbe"],"JavaScript":["JavaScript"],"Any JavaScript entered here will immediately run when your story is opened in a Web browser.":["Kakršna koli JavaScrip koda, ki jo vnesete sem, se bo izvedla takoj, ko zgodbo odprete v spletnem brskalniku."],"A passage already exists with this name.":["Prehod s tem imenom že obstaja."],"Tag":["Oznaka"],"Stylesheet":["Slogovna predloga"],"Any CSS entered here will override the default appearance of your story.":["Kakršni koli slogi CSS, ki jih vnesete sem, bodo spremenili privzeti videz vaše zgodbe."],"Please choose which language you would like to use with Twine.":["Prosim, izberite, v katerem jeziku bi radi uporabljali Twine."],"Hi!":["Pozdravljeni!"],"Twine is an open-source tool for telling interactive, nonlinear stories. There are a few things you should know before you get started.":["Twine je odprtokodno orodje za pripovedovanje interaktivnih nelinearnih zgodb. Preden začnete, si poglejte nekaj informacij."],"Tell Me More":["Več o tem"],"Skip":["Preskoči"],"New here?":["Še nimate izkušenj?"],"&lt;strong&gt;If you've never used Twine before,&lt;/strong&gt; then welcome! The &lt;a href=\\\"http://twinery.org/2guide\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;Twine 2 Guide&lt;/a&gt; and the official wiki in general, are a great place to learn. Keep in mind that some articles on the wiki at large were written for Twine 1, which is a little bit different than this version. But most of the concepts are the same.":["&lt;strong&gt;Če še nikoli prej niste uporabljali Twinea,&lt;/strong&gt; dobrodošli! &lt;a href=\\\"http://twinery.org/2guide\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;Vodič za Twine 2&lt;/a&gt; in uradno wiki spletno mesto (oboje v angleščini) sta odlična kraja za učenje. Imejte pa v mislih, da so bili nekateri razdelki na wiki spletnem mestu večidel napisani za Twine 1, ki je nekoliko drugačen od te različice. Toda večina konceptov je enakih."],"&lt;strong&gt;If you have used Twine 1 before,&lt;/strong&gt; the guide also has details on what has changed in this version. Chief among them is a new default story format, Harlowe. But if you find you prefer the Twine 1 scripting syntax, try using SugarCube instead.":["&lt;strong&gt;Če ste že uporabljali Twine 1,&lt;/strong&gt; ima vodič tudi nekaj podrobnosti o spremembah v tej različici. Glavna sprememba je kajpak nov privzeti zgodbeni format Harlowe. Če pa vam je ljubša kodna sintaksa iz Twinea 1, preizkusite raje SugarCube."],"OK":["V redu"],"Your work is automatically saved.":["Vaše delo je samodejno shranjeno."],"There's now a folder named Twine in your Documents folder. Inside that is a Stories folder, where all your work will be saved. Twine saves as you work, so you don't have to worry about remembering to save it yourself. You can always open the folder your stories are saved to by using the &lt;b&gt;Show Library&lt;/b&gt; item in the &lt;b&gt;Twine&lt;/b&gt; menu.":["V vaši mapi Dokumenti je sedaj mapa z naslovom Twine. V njej je mapa Stories, kamor bo shranjeno vse vaše delo. Twine shranjuje zgodbe, medtem ko delate, zato vam ni treba skrbeti za ročno shranjevanje. Do mape, kamor se zgodbe shranjujejo, lahko vedno dostopate prek opcije &lt;b&gt;Pokaži knjižnico&lt;/b&gt; v meniju &lt;b&gt;Twine&lt;/b&gt;."],"Because Twine is always saving your work, the files in your story library will be locked from editing while Twine is open.":["Ker Twine ves čas shranjuje vaše delo, datotek v vaši knjižnici ne bo mogoče urejati z drugimi programi, dokler je Twine odprt."],"That's it!":["To je vse!"],"Thanks for reading, and have fun with Twine.":["Hvala za vašo pozornost in veliko zabave s Twineom."],"Go to the Story List":["Pojdi na seznam zgodb"],"Test":["Testiraj"],"Play":["Predvajaj"],"Passage":["Prehod"],"Edit Story JavaScript":["Urejaj JavaScript"],"Edit Story Stylesheet":["Urejaj slogovno predlogo"],"Change Story Format":["Spremeni zgodbeni format"],"Rename Story":["Preimenuj zgodbo"],"Snap to Grid":["Pripni na mrežo"],"View Proofing Copy":["Poglej korekturno kopijo"],"Publish to File":["Izdaj v datoteko"],"Drop a story file to import":["Spustite sem zgodbeno datoteko za uvoz"],"Sort By":["Razvrsti po"],"Edit Date":["Uredi datum"],"Name":["Ime"],"There are no stories saved in Twine right now. To get started, you can either create a new story or import an existing one from a file.":["Trenutno v Twineu ni shranjenih nobenih zgodb. Lahko ali ustvarite novo zgodbo ali uvozite že obstoječo iz datoteke."],"Twine":["Twine"],"Story":["Zgodba"],"Archive":["Arhiv"],"Formats":["Formati"],"Language":["Jezik"],"Help":["Pomoč"],"version":["različica"],"Report a bug":["Prijavite hrošča"],"Play Story":["Predvajaj zgodbo"],"Test Story":["Testiraj zgodbo"],"Duplicate Story":["Podvoji zgodbo"],"Delete Story":["Izbriši zgodbo"],"&lt;strong&gt;If you've never used Twine before,&lt;/strong&gt; then welcome! The &lt;a href=\\\"http://twinery.org/2guide\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;Twine 2 Guide&lt;/a&gt; and the official wiki in general, are a great place to learn. Keep in mind that some articles on the wiki were written for Twine 1, which is a little bit different than this version. But most of the concepts are the same.":["&lt;strong&gt;Če še nikoli prej niste uporabljali Twinea,&lt;/strong&gt; dobrodošli! &lt;a href=\\\"http://twinery.org/2guide\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"&gt;Vodič za Twine 2&lt;/a&gt; in uradno wiki spletno mesto (oboje v angleščini) sta odlična kraja za učenje. Imejte pa v mislih, da so bili nekateri razdelki na wiki spletnem mestu večidel napisani za Twine 1, ki je nekoliko drugačen od te različice. Toda večina konceptov je enakih."],"Your work is saved only in your browser.":["Vaše delo je shranjeno samo v vašem brskalniku."],"That means you don't need to create an account to use Twine 2, and everything you create isn't stored on a server somewhere else &mdash; it stays right in your browser.":["To pomeni, da vam za uporabo Twinea 2 ni treba ustvarjati računa in da se vse, kar ustvarite, ne shranjuje na kak strežnik daleč stran, temveč ostane v vašem brskalniku."],"Two &lt;b&gt;very important&lt;/b&gt; things to remember, though. Since your work is saved only in your browser, if you clear its saved data, then you'll lose your work! Not good. Remember to use that &lt;i class=\\\"fa fa-briefcase\\\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Archive&lt;/strong&gt; button often. You can also publish individual stories to files using the &lt;i class=\\\"fa fa-cog\\\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; menu on each story in the story list. Both archive and story files can always be re-imported into Twine.":["Treba pa si je zapomniti dve &lt;b&gt;zelo pomembni&lt;/b&gt; stvari. Ker je vaše delo shranjeno samo v vašem brskalniku, boste, če pobrišete brskalnikove podatke, izgubili svoje delo! Dokaj neprijetna reč. Čim večkrat se spomnite klikniti na tisti &lt;i class=\\\"fa fa-briefcase\\\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Arhiv&lt;/strong&gt; gumbek. Prav tako lahko posamezne zgodbe izdate v datoteke s pomočjo menija &lt;i class=\\\"fa fa-cog\\\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; za vsako zgodbo na seznamu. Tako arhiv kot zgodbene datoteke lahko kadarkoli ponovno uvozite v Twine."],"Secondly, &lt;b&gt;anyone who can use this browser can see and make changes to your work&lt;/b&gt;. So if you've got a nosy kid brother, look into setting up a separate profile for yourself.":["In še druga stvar: &lt;b&gt;vsakdo, ki uporablja ta brskalnik, lahko vidi in spreminja vaše delo&lt;/b&gt;. Če imate torej firbčnega bratca, ki se vam mota naokoli, si raje omislite ločen profil zase."],"a more recent version of the story format &ldquo;%s&rdquo; is already installed":["Novejša različica zgodbenega formata &ldquo;%s&rdquo; je že nameščena"],"There is no starting point set for this story.":["Za to zgodbo ni nastavljena nobena začetna točka."],"The passage set as starting point for this story does not exist.":["Prehod, nastavljen kot začetna točka za to zgodbo, ne obstaja."],"Untitled Story Format":["Neimenovan zgodbeni format"],"Untitled Story":["Neimenovana zgodba"],"Untitled Passage":["Neimenovan prehod"],"Tap this passage, then the pencil icon to edit it.":["Kliknite to sporočilo, potem pa še ikono s svinčnikom, da ga uredite."],"Double-click this passage to edit it.":["Dvakrat kliknite to sporočilo, da ga uredite."],"A new version of Twine, <span class=\"version\"></span>, has been released.":["Izdana je bila nova različica Twinea, <span class=\"version\"></span>."],"Download":["Prenesi"],"Not Right Now":["Ne še zdaj"],"The story format &ldquo;%1$s&rdquo; could not be loaded (%2$s).":["Zgodbenega formata &ldquo;%1$s&rdquo; ni bilo mogoče naložiti (%2$s)."],"The story format at %1$s could not be added (%2$s).":["Zgodbenega formata pri %1$s ni bilo mogoče prenesti (%2$s)."],"by %s":["avtorja/ice %s"],"Are you sure?":["Ste prepričani?"],"Remove":["Odstrani"],"Don\\'t Replace Any Stories":["Ne zamenjaj nobenih zgodb"],"Replace %d Story":["Zamenjaj %d zgodbo","Zamenjaj %d zgodbi","Zamenjaj %d zgodbe","Zamenjaj %d zgodb"],"Character":["Znak","Znaka","Znaki","Znaki"],"Word":["Beseda","Besedi","Besede","Besede"],"Link":["Povezava","Povezavi","Povezave","Povezave"],"Broken Link":["Okvarjena povezava","Okvarjeni povezavi","Okvarjene povezave","Okvarjene povezave"],"Enter the body text of your passage here. To link to another passage, put two square brackets around its name, [[like this]].":["Sem vnesite jedrno besedilo vašega prehoda. Če ga hočete povezati z drugim prehodom, njegovo ime postavite v dvojne oglate oklepaje, [[tako]]."],"Editing \\u201c%s\\u201d":["Urejam \\u201c%s\\u201d"],"&ldquo;%1$s&rdquo; could not be saved (%2$s).":["Datoteke &ldquo;%1$s&rdquo; ni bilo mogoče shraniti (%2$s)."],"Documents":["Dokumenti"],"My\\\\ Documents":["Moji\\\\ dokumenti"],"Stories":["Zgodbe"],"Toggle Fullscreen":["Preklopi celozaslonski način"],"Quit":["Izhod"],"Edit":["Uredi"],"Undo":["Razveljavi"],"Cut":["Izreži"],"Copy":["Kopiraj"],"Paste":["Prilepi"],"Delete":["Izbriši"],"Show Library":["Pokaži knjižnico"],"Are you sure you want to delete &ldquo;%s&rdquo;? This cannot be undone.":["Res hočete izbrisati &ldquo;%s&rdquo;? Tega dejanja ni mogoče razveljaviti."],"(Hold the Shift key when deleting to skip this message.)":["(Če hočete preskočiti to sporočilo, med brisanjem držite tipko Shift.)"],"What should &ldquo;%s&rdquo; be renamed to?":["V kaj naj preimenujem &ldquo;%s&rdquo;?"],"Rename":["Preimenuj"],"Please enter a name.":["Prosim, vnesite ime."],"%d Story":["%d zgodba","%d zgodbi","%d zgodbe","%d zgodb"],"What should your story be named?<br>(You can change this later.)":["Kako naj bo ime vaši zgodbi?<br>(Ime lahko kasneje spremenite.)"],"A story with this name already exists.":["Zgodba s tem imenom že obstaja."],"Twine Archive.html":["Twine Arhiv.html"],"Delete Forever":["Izbriši za vedno"],"What should the duplicate be named?":["Kako naj bo ime dvojniku?"],"Duplicate":["Podvoji"],"%s Copy":["%s Kopiraj"],"%d%% space available":["%d%% nezasedenega prostora"]}}});